<html lang="it">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BrixIA</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/themes/dark.css">
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: white;
      }
      .container {
        background-image: url(https://api.brix-ia.com/uploads/Visual_Birxia_64749c8600.jpg);
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
      }
      .nav a {
        margin-left: 1rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.3s;
      }
      .nav a:hover {
        color: #38b2ac;
      }
      .main {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        background-image: url('/path/to/hero-background.jpg');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
      }
      .main h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }
      .main p {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }
      .buttons {
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
      .buttons button {
        background-color: var(--color-primary);
        margin: 0 0.5rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
        border-radius: 0.375rem;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
        color: var(--color-white);
      }
      .buttons .primary {
        color: #1a202c;
      }
      .buttons .primary:hover {
        background-color: var(--color-accent);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
      <div class="container">   
            <main class="main">
                <h1>
                    Inizia oggi la tua nuova carriera
                    <br />
                    <span>nel mondo dei dati e dell'AI</span>
                </h1>
                <p>
                Impara oggi le competenze necessarie per garantirti un futuro allâ€™altezza dei tuoi desideri.
            </p>
            <div class="buttons">
                <button class="primary">Iscriviti</button>
                <button class="primary">Inizia il test</button>
                </div>
            </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
